sources.description:
Legacy: While on a hunting trip in the isolated wilderness, a father and his adopted teenage son are turned into the prey of unknown assailants. They are unexpectedly joined in their fight for survival by a stranger who reveals the disturbing truth about the son's biological father, an international crime lord, and why that crime lord has sent trained assassins to kill the teenager.
2020.  Stars: Luke Goss, Louis Mandylor, Elya Baskin

Your Move: A man must go to extreme lengths to discover what happened to his kidnapped wife and daughter.
2017.  Stars: Robert Davi, Luke Goss, Patricia De Leon
